        "created_at": "2021-10-09T12:12:41.245Z",
        "cooked": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/apple/foundationdb/blob/ddf85af360c8e38dc454dbd8c481ef2a7efddacb/fdbserver/Resolver.actor.cpp#L45\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a> the data structure to maintain some states for resolver is used as a reference, but <a href=\"https://github.com/apple/foundationdb/blob/ddf85af360c8e38dc454dbd8c481ef2a7efddacb/fdbserver/MasterProxyServer.actor.cpp#L590\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a> the data structure to maintain inner states for proxy is used as a pointer, what\u2019s the logic for u to decide when to use Reference and when to just use pointer?</p>",
